{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"003949dea7","title":"给全体同学的一封信","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f4e532c64","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":21,"articleId":"003949dea7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"01707aff9c","name":"杨金访"},{"id":"089c6b4fa3","name":"杨铭"},{"id":"0c430b6e51","name":"山西医学院"},{"id":"693ffff67e","name":"贾受业"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c9235bb027","type":"title","text":"给全体同学的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"75fe887097","type":"authors","text":"山西医学院杨金访贾受业杨铭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"f74c1c90d4","type":"subtitle","text":"(杨金访、贾受业、杨铭：山西医学院医疗系22班学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"820beaf33c","type":"subtitle","text":"医22班给全体同学的一封信","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"374000f34f","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们：根据目前情况，根据历来的教训，现在的争鸣方式和整风办公室已经不能全面代表同学们的意见了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"007716c624","type":"paragraph","text":"为了鸣放彻底，为了让鸣放取到应有的效果，为了使我们的意见得到重视和得到解决，为了彻底消灭我院的三大主义，为了使高教部、卫生部听到同学们的真正呼声，为了有一个真正的全面代表同学们的利益的组织，我们建议每班选一至二人成立同学鸣放委员会，这个委员会直接和中央取得联系，这个委员会：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"1f6dd0d477","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，研究院领导的三大主义和院领导的能力问题。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"b77e893cb8","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，领导同学向高教部和卫生部争取师资和教学设备，争取扩充必要的基本建设。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"334caae8f8","type":"paragraph","text":"第三，讨论高教部和卫生部对我院的态度问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"5de627493f","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，研究其它急需解决的问题。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"c6091058a1","type":"paragraph","text":"第五，研究出一个具体措施保证以上诸问题得到圆满解决。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"},{"id":"cad62342cb","type":"paragraph","text":" 医疗系22班全体同学1957年6月21日","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7"}],"page":{"id":"805ab99fd0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"003949dea7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}